body_html:
Hi,

I just pushed a new commit that fixes the issue with the missing op kernel. It looks like new defines left out the implementation and registration of the op during the compilation due to missing defines in compiler command line. I also added a small test script to validate the functionality of the workflow.

@aaroey and @wujingyue, if you are happy with the changes, I think we can continue to the next step.

Thanks,
Sami
